9 \file dump.c
10 \brief dump routines for compiler's internal data structures.
11 This file contains dump routines for the compiler's various internal
12 data structures (e.g., symbol tables, dtype records, etc.).

29#if DEBUG
30static FILE *dfile;
31static int linelen = 0;
32static char BUF[900];
33
34static int longlines = 1;
35
36static void
37putit()
38{
39 int l = strlen(BUF);
40 if (linelen + l >= 78 && !longlines) {
41 fprintf(dfile, "\n%s", BUF);
42 linelen = l;
43 } else if (linelen > 0) {
44 fprintf(dfile, " %s", BUF);
45 linelen += l + 2;
46 } else {
47 fprintf(dfile, "%s", BUF);
48 linelen = l;
49 }
50} /* putit */
51
52static void
53appendit()
54{
55 int l = strlen(BUF);
56 fprintf(dfile, "%s", BUF);
57 linelen += l;
58} /* appendit */
59
60static void
61putline()
62{
63 if (linelen)
64 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
65 linelen = 0;
66} /* putline */
67
68static void
69putint(const char *s, int d)
70{
71 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d", s, d);
72 putit();
73} /* putint */

145static void
146putnzbits(const char *s, int d)
147{
148 if (d != 0) {
149 char *b;
150 int any = 0;
151 sprintf(BUF, "%s:", s);
152 b = BUF + strlen(BUF);
153 while (d) {
154 if (d & 0x8000000) {
155 *b = '1';
156 ++b;
157 any = 1;
158 } else if (any) {
159 *b = '0';
160 ++b;
161 }
162 d = d << 1;
163 }
164 *b = '\0';
165 putit();
166 }
167} /* putnzbits */

183static void
184putsym(const char *s, int sptr)
185{
186 if (sptr == NOSYM) {
187 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d=%s", s, sptr, "NOSYM");
188 } else if (sptr > 0 && sptr < stb.stg_avail) {
189 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d=%s", s, sptr, SYMNAME(sptr));
190 } else {
191 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d", s, sptr);
192 }
193 putit();
194} /* putsym */

224static void

226{

228 putsym1(SYMI_SPTR(symi));

232void
233dumpsymi(int symi)
234{
235 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
236 if (symi <= 0 || symi >= aux.symi_avl) {
237 fprintf(dfile, "\nsymi %d out of %d\n", symi, aux.symi_avl);
238 return;
239 }
240 putint("symi", symi);
241 putsymilist(symi);
242 putline();
243} /* dumpsymi */
244
245static void
246putnsym(const char *s, int sptr)
247{
248 if (sptr == NOSYM) {
249 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d=%s", s, sptr, "NOSYM");
250 putit();
251 } else if (sptr > 0 && sptr < stb.stg_avail) {
252 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_CONST) {
253 if (DTY(DTYPEG(sptr)) == TY_CHAR) {
254 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d=%s", s, sptr, stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr));
255 } else {
256 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d", s, sptr);
257 }
258 } else {
259 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d=%s", s, sptr, SYMNAME(sptr));
260 }
261 putit();
262 } else {
263 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d", s, sptr);
264 putit();
265 }
266} /* putnsym */

322#ifdef CUDAG
323static void
324putcuda(const char *s, int cu)
325{
326 if (cu) {
327 strcpy(BUF, s);
328 strcat(BUF, ":");
329 if (cu & CUDA_HOST) {
330 strcat(BUF, "host");
331 cu &= ~CUDA_HOST;
332 if (cu)
333 strcat(BUF, "+");
334 }
335 if (cu & CUDA_GRID) {
336 strcat(BUF, "grid");
337 cu &= ~CUDA_GRID;
338 if (cu)
339 strcat(BUF, "+");
340 }
341 if (cu & CUDA_DEVICE) {
342 strcat(BUF, "device");
343 cu &= ~CUDA_DEVICE;
344 if (cu)
345 strcat(BUF, "+");
346 }
347 if (cu & CUDA_GLOBAL) {
348 strcat(BUF, "global");
349 cu &= ~CUDA_GLOBAL;
350 if (cu)
351 strcat(BUF, "+");
352 }
353 if (cu & CUDA_BUILTIN) {
354 strcat(BUF, "builtin");
355 cu &= ~CUDA_BUILTIN;
356 if (cu)
357 strcat(BUF, "+");
358 }
359 putit();
360 }
361} /* putcuda */
362#endif

364static void
365putintent(const char *s, int intent)
366{
367 switch (intent) {
368 case 0:
369 break;
370 case 1:
371 sprintf(BUF, "%s:in", s);
372 putit();
373 break;
374 case 2:
375 sprintf(BUF, "%s:out", s);
376 putit();
377 break;
378 case 3:
379 sprintf(BUF, "%s:inout", s);
380 putit();
381 break;
382 default:
383 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d", s, intent);
384 putit();
385 break;
386 }
387} /* putintent */

389static void
390putinkind(const char *s, int k)
391{
392 switch (k) {
393 case IK_ELEMENTAL:
394 putstring(s, "elemental");
395 break;
396 case IK_INQUIRY:
397 putstring(s, "inquiry");
398 break;
399 case IK_TRANSFORM:
400 putstring(s, "transform");
401 break;
402 case IK_SUBROUTINE:
403 putstring(s, "subroutine");
404 break;
405 default:
406 putint(s, k);
407 break;
408 }
409} /* putinkind */

440{

449static void
450putparam(int dpdsc, int paramct)
451{
452 if (paramct == 0)
453 return;
454 putline();
455 putstring1("Parameters:");
456 for (; dpdsc && paramct; ++dpdsc, --paramct) {
457 int sptr = aux.dpdsc_base[dpdsc];
458 if (sptr == 0) {
459 putstring1("*");
460 } else {
461 putsym1(sptr);
462 }
463 }
464} /* putparam */

466void
467putsymlk(const char *name, int list)
468{
469 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
470 if (list <= NOSYM)
471 return;
472 putline();
473 putstring1(name);
474 for (; list > NOSYM; list = SYMLKG(list)) {
475 putsym1(list);
476 }
477} /* putsymlk */
478
479void
480putslnk1(int list)
481{
482 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
483 if (list <= NOSYM)
484 return;
485 for (; list > NOSYM; list = SLNKG(list)) {
486 putsym1(list);
487 }
488} /* putslnk1 */
489
490void
491dumplists()
492{
493 int stype;
494 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
495 for (stype = 0; stype <= ST_MAX; ++stype) {
496 if (aux.list[stype] > NOSYM) {
497 putstring1("aux.list[");
498 putstype1(stype);
499 appendstring1("] =");
500 putslnk1(aux.list[stype]);
501 putline();
502 }
503 }
504} /* dumplists */

587static void
588putbit(const char *s, int b)
589{
590 /* single space between flags */
591 if (b) {
592 int l = strlen(s);
593 if (linelen + l >= 78 && !longlines) {
594 fprintf(dfile, "\n%s", s);
595 linelen = l;
596 } else if (linelen > 0) {
597 fprintf(dfile, " %s", s);
598 linelen += l + 1;
599 } else {
600 fprintf(dfile, "%s", s);
601 linelen = l;
602 }
603 }
604} /* putbit */

606static void
607check(const char *s, int v)
608{
609 if (v) {
610 fprintf(dfile, "*** %s: %d 0x%x\n", s, v, v);
611 }
612} /* check */

615static void
616putmap(char *s, int m)
617{
618 /* single space between flags */
619 switch (m) {
620 case PRESCRIPTIVE:
621 putstring(s, "prescriptive");
622 break;
623 case DESCRIPTIVE:
624 putstring(s, "descriptive");
625 break;
626 case TRANSCRIPTIVE:
627 putstring(s, "transcriptive");
628 break;
629 default:
630 sprintf(BUF, "%s:(%d)", s, m);
631 putit();
632 }
633} /* putmap */
634#endif

636void
637putasttype(const char *s, int opc)
638{
639 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
640 if (opc < 0 || opc > AST_MAX) {
641 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d", s, opc);
642 } else {
643 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d:%s", s, opc, astb.atypes[opc]);
644 }
645 putit();
646} /* putasttype */
647
648static void
649putast(const char *s, int a)
650{
651 if (a == 0)
652 return;
653 if (a < 0 || a >= astb.stg_avail) {
654 if (s && *s) {
655 sprintf(BUF, "(%s=%d)", s, a);
656 } else {
657 sprintf(BUF, "(%d)", a);
658 }
659 putit();
660 return;
661 }
662 if (linelen + 2 >= 78 && !longlines) {
663 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
664 linelen = 1;
665 } else if (linelen > 0) {
666 fprintf(dfile, " ");
667 linelen += 1;
668 }
669 if (s && *s) {
670 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d=", s, a);
671 putit();
672 }
673 printast(a);
674} /* putast */
675
676static void
677putval(const char *s, int val, const char *values[], int sizeofvalues)
678{
679 if (val < 0 || val >= sizeofvalues) {
680 sprintf(BUF, "%s:%d", s, val);
681 putit();
682 } else {
683 putstring(s, values[val]);
684 }
685} /* putval */

687#define SIZEOF(array) (sizeof(array) / sizeof(char *))

689static void
690putoptype(const char *s, int optype)
691{
692 static const char *opt[] = {
693 "neg", "add", "sub", "mul", "div", "xtoi", "xtox",
694 "cmp", "aif", "ld", "st", "func", "con", "cat",
695 "log", "leqv", "lneqv", "lor", "land", "eq", "ge",
696 "gt", "le", "lt", "ne", "lnot", "loc", "ref",
697 "val", "scand", "scalar", "array", "derived"};
698 putval(s, optype, opt, SIZEOF(opt));
699} /* putoptype */

701void
702dastli(int astli)
703{
704 int a;
705 for (a = astli; a; a = ASTLI_NEXT(a)) {
706 if (a <= 0 || a > astb.astli.stg_avail) {
707 sprintf(BUF, "badastli:%d", a);
708 putit();
709 } else {
710 sprintf(BUF, "%d:%d:%d:0x%4.4x", a, ASTLI_SPTR(a), ASTLI_TRIPLE(a),
711 ASTLI_FLAGS(a));
712 }
713 }
714} /* dastli */

716void
717dast(int astx)
718{
719 int atype, dtype, asdx, j, argcnt, args, astli;
720 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
721 if (astx < 0 || astx >= astb.stg_avail) {
722 fprintf(dfile, "\nast %d out of range [0:%d)\n", astx, astb.stg_avail);
723 return;
724 }
725 putint("ast", astx);
726
727 BCOPY(astb.stg_base, astb.stg_base + astx, AST, 1);
728
729 atype = A_TYPEG(0);
730 putasttype("atype", atype);
731 putint("hashlk/std", A_HSHLKG(0));
732 putint("shape", A_SHAPEG(0));
733
734 switch (atype) {
735 case A_ID:
736 case A_CNST:
737 case A_BINOP:
738 case A_UNOP:
739 case A_CMPLXC:
740 case A_CONV:
741 case A_PAREN:
742 case A_MEM:
743 case A_SUBSCR:
744 case A_SUBSTR:
745 case A_FUNC:
746 case A_INTR:
747 case A_INIT:
748 case A_ASN:
749 dtype = A_DTYPEG(0);
750 putdtype("dtype", dtype);
751 break;
752 }
753 switch (atype) {
754 case A_ID:
755 case A_BINOP:
756 case A_UNOP:
757 case A_CMPLXC:
758 case A_CONV:
759 case A_PAREN:
760 case A_SUBSTR:
761 case A_FUNC:
762 case A_INTR:
763 putnzint("alias", A_ALIASG(0));
764 A_ALIASP(0, 0);
765 putbit("callfg", A_CALLFGG(0));
766 A_CALLFGP(0, 0);
767 break;
768 }
769 putnzint("opt1", A_OPT1G(0));
770 A_OPT1P(0, 0);
771 putnzint("opt2", A_OPT2G(0));
772 A_OPT2P(0, 0);
773 switch (atype) {
774 case A_NULL:
775 break;
776 case A_ID:
777 case A_LABEL:
778 case A_ENTRY:
779 putsym("sptr", A_SPTRG(0));
780 A_SPTRP(0, 0);
781 break;
782 case A_CNST:
783 putsym("sptr", A_SPTRG(0));
784 A_SPTRP(0, 0);
785 break;
786 case A_BINOP:
787 putoptype("optype", A_OPTYPEG(0));
788 A_OPTYPEP(0, 0);
789 putint("lop", A_LOPG(0));
790 A_LOPP(0, 0);
791 putint("rop", A_ROPG(astx));
792 A_LOPP(0, 0);
793 break;
794 case A_UNOP:
795 putoptype("optype", A_OPTYPEG(astx));
796 A_OPTYPEP(0, 0);
797 putint("lop", A_LOPG(astx));
798 A_LOPP(0, 0);
799 putbit("ptr0", astx == astb.ptr0);
800 putbit("ptr1", astx == astb.ptr1);
801 putbit("ptr0c", astx == astb.ptr0c);
802 break;
803 case A_CMPLXC:
804 putint("lop", A_LOPG(0));
805 A_LOPP(0, 0);
806 putint("rop", A_ROPG(astx));
807 A_LOPP(0, 0);
808 break;
809 case A_CONV:
810 putint("lop", A_LOPG(0));
811 A_LOPP(0, 0);
812 break;
813 case A_PAREN:
814 putint("lop", A_LOPG(0));
815 A_LOPP(0, 0);
816 break;
817 case A_MEM:
818 putint("parent", A_PARENTG(0));

1366void
1367dumpasts()
1368{
1369 int astx;
1370 for (astx = 1; astx < astb.stg_avail; ++astx) {

1372 }
1373} /* dumpasts */
1374
1375void
1376dumpshape(int shd)
1377{
1378 int nd, ii;
1379 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
1380 if (shd < 0 || shd >= astb.shd.stg_avail) {
1381 fprintf(dfile, "\nshd %d out of range [0:%d)\n", shd, astb.shd.stg_avail);
1382 return;
1383 }
1384 putint("shd", shd);
1385 nd = SHD_NDIM(shd);
1386 putint("ndim", nd);
1387 for (ii = 0; ii < nd; ++ii) {
1388 putline();
1389 putint("dim", ii);
1390 putast("lwb", SHD_LWB(shd, ii));
1391 putast("upb", SHD_UPB(shd, ii));
1392 putast("stride", SHD_STRIDE(shd, ii));
1393 }
1394 putline();
1395} /* dumpshape */
1396
1397void
1398dumpshapes()
1399{
1400 int shd;
1401 for (shd = 1; shd < astb.shd.stg_avail;) {
1402 if (shd > 1) {
1403 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
1404 }
1405 dumpshape(shd);
1406 shd += 1 + SHD_NDIM(shd);
1407 }
1408} /* dumpshapes */
1409
1410static char prefix[500];
1411
1412static void
1413dastreex(int astx, int l, int notlast)
1414{
1415 int asdx, ndim, j, args, argcnt;
1416 if (astx == 0)
1417 return;
1418 if (l > 4)
1419 strcpy(prefix + l - 4, "+-- ");
1420 fprintf(dfile, "%s", prefix);
1421 dast(astx);
1422 if (astx <= 0 || astx >= astb.stg_avail)
1423 return;
1424 if (l) {
1425 if (notlast) {
1426 strcpy(prefix + l - 4, "| ");
1427 } else {
1428 strcpy(prefix + l - 4, " ");
1429 }
1430 }
1431 switch (A_TYPEG(astx)) {
1432 case A_NULL:
1433 case A_ID:
1434 case A_LABEL:
1435 case A_ENTRY:
1436 case A_CNST:
1437 case A_CMPLXC:
1438 case A_GOTO:
1439 case A_CGOTO:
1440 case A_AGOTO:
1441 break;
1442 case A_BINOP:
1443 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1444 dastreex(A_ROPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1445 break;
1446 case A_MEM:
1447 dastreex(A_MEMG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1448 dastreex(A_PARENTG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1449 break;
1450 case A_CONV:
1451 case A_UNOP:
1452 case A_PAREN:
1453 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1454 break;
1455 case A_SUBSCR:
1456 asdx = A_ASDG(astx);
1457 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asdx);
1458 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, ndim > 0);
1459 for (j = 0; j < ndim; ++j) {
1460 dastreex(ASD_SUBS(asdx, j), l + 4, ndim - j - 1);
1461 }
1462 break;
1463 case A_SUBSTR:
1464 dastreex(A_LEFTG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1465 dastreex(A_RIGHTG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1466 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1467 break;
1468 case A_INIT:
1469 dastreex(A_LEFTG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1470 dastreex(A_RIGHTG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1471 break;
1472 case A_TRIPLE:
1473 dastreex(A_LBDG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1474 dastreex(A_UPBDG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1475 dastreex(A_STRIDEG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1476 break;
1477 case A_FUNC:
1478 case A_INTR:
1479 case A_CALL:
1480 case A_ICALL:
1481 argcnt = A_ARGCNTG(astx);
1482 args = A_ARGSG(astx);
1483 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, argcnt > 0);
1484 for (j = 0; j < argcnt; ++j) {
1485 dastreex(ARGT_ARG(args, j), l + 4, argcnt - j - 1);
1486 }
1487 break;
1488 case A_ASN:
1489 case A_ASNGOTO:
1490 dastreex(A_DESTG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1491 dastreex(A_SRCG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1492 break;
1493 case A_IF:
1494 dastreex(A_IFEXPRG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1495 dastreex(A_IFSTMTG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1496 break;
1497 case A_IFTHEN:
1498 dastreex(A_IFEXPRG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1499 break;
1500 case A_ELSE:
1501 break;
1502 case A_ELSEIF:
1503 dastreex(A_IFEXPRG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1504 break;
1505 case A_ENDIF:
1506 break;
1507 case A_AIF:
1508 dastreex(A_IFEXPRG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1509 break;
1510 case A_DO:
1511 dastreex(A_M1G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1512 dastreex(A_M2G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1513 dastreex(A_M3G(astx), l + 4, 0);
1514 dastreex(A_M4G(astx), l + 4, 0);
1515 break;
1516 case A_DOWHILE:
1517 dastreex(A_IFEXPRG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1518 break;
1519 case A_ENDDO:
1520 case A_CONTINUE:
1521 case A_END:
1522 break;
1523 case A_STOP:
1524 case A_PAUSE:
1525 case A_RETURN:
1526 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1527 break;
1528 case A_ALLOC:
1529 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1530 dastreex(A_SRCG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1531 dastreex(A_DESTG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1532 dastreex(A_M3G(astx), l + 4, 0);
1533 dastreex(A_STARTG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1534 dastreex(A_DTYPEG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1535 break;
1536 case A_WHERE:
1537 dastreex(A_IFEXPRG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1538 dastreex(A_IFSTMTG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1539 break;
1540 case A_FORALL:
1541 break;
1542 case A_ELSEWHERE:
1543 case A_ENDWHERE:
1544 case A_ENDFORALL:
1545 case A_ELSEFORALL:
1546 break;
1547 case A_REDIM:
1548 break;
1549 case A_COMMENT:
1550 case A_COMSTR:
1551 break;
1552 case A_REALIGN:
1553 case A_REDISTRIBUTE:
1554 break;
1555 case A_HLOCALIZEBNDS:
1556 break;
1557 case A_HALLOBNDS:
1558 break;
1559 case A_HCYCLICLP:
1560 break;
1561 case A_HOFFSET:
1562 break;
1563 case A_HSECT:
1564 break;
1565 case A_HCOPYSECT:
1566 break;
1567 case A_HPERMUTESECT:
1568 break;
1569 case A_HOVLPSHIFT:
1570 break;
1571 case A_HGETSCLR:
1572 dastreex(A_DESTG(astx), l + 4, 1);
1573 dastreex(A_SRCG(astx), l + 4, A_LOPG(astx));
1574 if (A_LOPG(astx)) {
1575 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1576 }
1577 break;
1578 case A_HGATHER:
1579 case A_HSCATTER:
1580 break;
1581 case A_HCSTART:
1582 break;
1583 case A_HCFINISH:
1584 case A_HCFREE:
1585 break;
1586 case A_MASTER:
1587 break;
1588 case A_ENDMASTER:
1589 argcnt = A_ARGCNTG(astx);
1590 args = A_ARGSG(astx);
1591 for (j = 0; j < argcnt; ++j) {
1592 dastreex(ARGT_ARG(args, j), l + 4, argcnt - j - 1);
1593 }
1594 break;
1595 case A_ATOMIC:
1596 case A_PREFETCH:
1597 case A_PRAGMA:
1598 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1599 break;
1600 case A_CRITICAL:
1601 case A_ENDCRITICAL:
1602 case A_ENDATOMIC:
1603 case A_BARRIER:
1604 case A_NOBARRIER:
1605 break;
1606 case A_MP_TARGET:
1607 case A_MP_TARGETUPDATE:
1608 case A_MP_TARGETDATA:
1609 case A_MP_TARGETENTERDATA:
1610 case A_MP_TARGETEXITDATA:
1611 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
1612 dastreex(A_IFPARG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1613 break;
1614 case A_MP_TEAMS:
1615 dastreex(A_NTEAMSG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1616 dastreex(A_THRLIMITG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1617 break;
1618 case A_MP_BMPSCOPE:
1619 dastreex(A_STBLKG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1620 break;
1621 case A_MP_TASK:
1622 case A_MP_TASKLOOP:
1623 dastreex(A_IFPARG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1624 break;
1625 case A_MP_TASKFIRSTPRIV:
1626 case A_MP_ENDPARALLEL:
1627 case A_MP_CRITICAL:
1628 case A_MP_ENDCRITICAL:
1629 case A_MP_ATOMIC:
1630 case A_MP_ENDATOMIC:
1631 case A_MP_MASTER:
1632 case A_MP_ENDMASTER:
1633 case A_MP_SINGLE:
1634 case A_MP_ENDSINGLE:
1635 case A_MP_BARRIER:
1636 case A_MP_ETASKDUP:
1637 case A_MP_ETASKLOOPREG:
1638 case A_MP_TASKWAIT:
1639 case A_MP_TASKYIELD:
1640 case A_MP_ENDTASK:
1641 case A_MP_ETASKLOOP:
1642 case A_MP_EMPSCOPE:
1643 case A_MP_ENDTARGET:
1644 case A_MP_ENDTEAMS:
1645 case A_MP_ENDDISTRIBUTE:
1646 case A_MP_ENDTARGETDATA:
1647 case A_MP_TASKDUP:
1648 break;
1649 case A_MP_ATOMICREAD:
1650 dastreex(A_SRCG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1651 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
1652 case A_MP_ATOMICWRITE:
1653 case A_MP_ATOMICUPDATE:
1654 case A_MP_ATOMICCAPTURE:
1655 dastreex(A_LOPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1656 dastreex(A_ROPG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1657 break;
1658 case A_MP_TASKREG:
1659 dastreex(A_ENDLABG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1660 break;
1661 case A_MP_TASKLOOPREG:
1662 dastreex(A_M1G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1663 dastreex(A_M2G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1664 dastreex(A_M3G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1665 break;
1666 case A_MP_CANCEL:
1667 dastreex(A_IFPARG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1668 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
1669 case A_MP_SECTIONS:
1670 case A_MP_CANCELLATIONPOINT:
1671 dastreex(A_ENDLABG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1672 break;
1673 case A_MP_PDO:
1674 dastreex(A_M1G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1675 dastreex(A_M2G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1676 dastreex(A_M3G(astx), l + 4, 1);
1677 dastreex(A_CHUNKG(astx), l + 4, 0);
1678 break;
1679 case A_MP_ENDPDO:
1680 case A_MP_ENDSECTIONS:
1681 case A_MP_SECTION:
1682 case A_MP_LSECTION:
1683 case A_MP_PRE_TLS_COPY:
1684 case A_MP_BCOPYIN:
1685 case A_MP_COPYIN:
1686 case A_MP_ECOPYIN:
1687 case A_MP_BCOPYPRIVATE:
1688 case A_MP_COPYPRIVATE:
1689 case A_MP_ECOPYPRIVATE:
1690 case A_MP_MAP:
1691 case A_MP_EMAP:
1692 case A_MP_TARGETLOOPTRIPCOUNT:
1693 case A_MP_DISTRIBUTE:
1694 case A_MP_EREDUCTION:
1695 case A_MP_BREDUCTION:
1696 case A_MP_REDUCTIONITEM:
1697 break;
1698 default:
1699 fprintf(gbl.dbgfil, "NO DUMP AVL");
1700 break;
1701 }
1702 prefix[l - 4] = '\0';
1703} /* dastreex */

1717 dastreex(astx, 4, 0);
1718 prefix[0] = '\0';
1719 longlines = savelonglines;
1720} /* dastree */

1739void
1740dumpfnode(int v)
1741{
1742 PSI_P succ, pred;
1743 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
1744 if (opt.fgb.stg_base == NULL) {
1745 fprintf(dfile, "OPT.FGB.STG not allocated\n");
1746 return;
1747 }
1748 if (v < 0 || v > opt.num_nodes) {
1749 fprintf(dfile, "Flow graph node %d out of %d\n", v, opt.num_nodes);
1750 return;
1751 }
1752 putint("fnode", v);
1753 putint("lineno", FG_LINENO(v));
1754 putnsym("label", FG_LABEL(v));
1755 putnzint("lprev", FG_LPREV(v));
1756 putnzint("lnext", FG_LNEXT(v));
1757 putnzint("first", FG_STDFIRST(v));
1758 putnzint("last", FG_STDLAST(v));
1759 putnzint("atomic", FG_ATOMIC(v));
1760 putnzint("dfn", FG_DFN(v));
1761 putnzint("dom", FG_DOM(v));
1762 putnzint("pdom", FG_PDOM(v));
1763 putnzint("loop", FG_LOOP(v));
1764 putnzint("next", FG_NEXT(v));
1765 putnzint("natnxt", FG_NATNXT(v));
1766 putnzint("par", FG_PAR(v));
1767 putnzint("parloop", FG_PARLOOP(v));
1768 putline();
1769 pred = FG_PRED(v);
1770 if (pred == NULL) {
1771 putstring("pred", "none");
1772 } else {
1773 putstring1("pred:");
1774 for (; pred != PSI_P_NULL; pred = PSI_NEXT(pred)) {
1775 putint1star(PSI_NODE(pred), PSI_FT(pred), "(ft)");
1776 }
1777 }
1778 succ = FG_SUCC(v);
1779 if (succ == NULL) {
1780 putstring("succ", "none");
1781 } else {
1782 putstring1("succ:");
1783 for (; succ != PSI_P_NULL; succ = PSI_NEXT(succ)) {
1784 putint1star(PSI_NODE(succ), PSI_FT(succ), "(ft)");
1785 }
1786 }
1787 putline();
1788 putbit("call", FG_EX(v));
1789 putbit("cs", FG_CS(v));
1790 putbit("ctlequiv", FG_CTLEQUIV(v));
1791 putbit("entry", FG_EN(v));
1792 putbit("exit", FG_XT(v));
1793 putbit("fallthru", FG_FT(v));
1794 putbit("head", FG_HEAD(v));
1795 putbit("innermost", FG_INNERMOST(v));
1796 putbit("jumptable", FG_JMP_TBL(v));
1797 putbit("master", FG_MASTER(v));
1798 putbit("mexits", FG_MEXITS(v));
1799 putbit("parsect", FG_PARSECT(v));
1800 putbit("task", FG_TASK(v));
1801 putbit("ptrstore", FG_PTR_STORE(v));
1802 putbit("tail", FG_TAIL(v));
1803 putbit("zerotrip", FG_ZTRP(v));
1804 putline();
1805} /* dumpfnode */

1808dumpfg(int v)
1809{
1810 dumpfnode(v);
1811} /* dumpfg */
1812
1813void
1814dfg(int v)
1815{
1816 dumpfnode(v);

1819void
1820dumpfgraph()
1821{
1822 int v;
1823 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
1824 if (opt.fgb.stg_base == NULL) {
1825 fprintf(dfile, "OPT.FGB.STG not allocated\n");
1826 return;
1827 }
1828 for (v = 1; v <= opt.num_nodes; ++v) {
1829 if (v > 1)
1830 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
1831 dumpfnode(v);
1832 }
1833
1834 fprintf(dfile, "\nDepth First Order:\n");
1835 for (v = 1; v <= opt.dfn; ++v) {
1836 putint1(VTX_NODE(v));
1837 }
1838 putline();
1839
1840 fprintf(dfile, "\nRetreating Edges:\n");
1841 for (v = 0; v < opt.rteb.stg_avail; ++v) {
1842 putedge(EDGE_PRED(v), EDGE_SUCC(v));
1843 }
1844 putline();
1845} /* dumpfgraph */

1847void
1848putnme(int n)
1849{
1850 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
1851 if (n < 0 || n >= nmeb.stg_avail) {
1852 putint("nme", n);
1853 return;
1854 }
1855 switch (NME_TYPE(n)) {
1856 case NT_VAR:
1857 putstring1(getprint(NME_SYM(n)));
1858 break;
1859 case NT_MEM:
1860 putnme(NME_NM(n));
1861 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
1862 appendstring1(".real");
1863 break;
1864 }
1865 if (NME_SYM(n) == 1) {
1866 appendstring1(".imag");
1867 break;
1868 }
1869 appendstring1(".");
1870 appendstring1(getprint(NME_SYM(n)));
1871 break;
1872 default:
1873 put2int("nme", n, NME_TYPE(n));
1874 break;
1875 }
1876} /* putnme */

1878void
1879putnmetype(const char *s, int t)
1880{
1881 switch (t) {
1882 case NT_ADD:
1883 putstring(s, "add");
1884 break;
1885 case NT_UNK: /* unknown */
1886 putstring(s, "unk");
1887 break;
1888 case NT_IND: /* Indirect ref e.g. *p */
1889 putstring(s, "ind");
1890 break;
1891 case NT_VAR: /* Variable ref. (struct, array or scalar) */
1892 putstring(s, "var");
1893 break;
1894 case NT_MEM: /* Structure member ref. */
1895 putstring(s, "mem");
1896 break;
1897 case NT_ARR: /* Array element ref. */
1898 putstring(s, "arr");
1899 break;
1900 case NT_SAFE: /* special names; does not conflict with preceding refs */
1901 putstring(s, "safe");
1902 break;
1903 default:
1904 putint(s, t);
1905 break;
1906 }
1907} /* putnmetype */
1908
1909char *
1910printname(int sptr)
1911{
1912 static char b[200];
1913
1914 if (sptr <= 0 || sptr >= stb.stg_avail) {
1915 sprintf(b, "symbol %d out of %d", sptr, stb.stg_avail - 1);
1916 return b;
1917 }
1918
1919 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_CONST) {
1920 INT num[2];
1921 int pointee;
1922 char *bb;
1923 switch (DTY(DTYPEG(sptr))) {
1924 case TY_INT8:
1925 num[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
1926 num[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
1927 ui64toax(num, b, 22, 0, 10);
1928 break;
1929 case TY_INT:
1930 sprintf(b, "%10d", CONVAL2G(sptr));
1931 break;
1932
1933 case TY_FLOAT:
1934 num[0] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
1935 cprintf(b, "%.8e", num);
1936 break;
1937
1938 case TY_QUAD:
1939 case TY_DBLE:
1940 num[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
1941 num[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
1942 cprintf(b, "%.17le", num);
1943 break;
1944
1945 case TY_PTR:
1946 pointee = CONVAL1G(sptr);
1947 if (pointee > 0 && pointee < stb.stg_avail && STYPEG(pointee) != ST_CONST) {
1948 if (CONVAL2G(sptr) == 0) {
1949 sprintf(b, "*%s", SYMNAME(pointee));
1950 } else {
1951 sprintf(b, "*%s+%d", SYMNAME(pointee), CONVAL2G(sptr));
1952 }
1953 } else {
1954 if (CONVAL2G(sptr) == 0) {
1955 sprintf(b, "*(sym %d)", pointee);
1956 } else {
1957 sprintf(b, "*(sym %d)+%d", pointee, CONVAL2G(sptr));
1958 }
1959 }
1960 break;
1961
1962 case TY_WORD:
1963 sprintf(b, "%10d", CONVAL2G(sptr));
1964 break;
1965
1966 case TY_CHAR:
1967 return stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr);
1968 break;
1969
1970 default:
1971 sprintf(b, "unknown constant %d dty %" ISZ_PF "d", sptr,
1972 DTY(DTYPEG(sptr)));
1973 break;
1974 }
1975 for (bb = b; *bb == ' '; ++bb)
1976 ;
1977 return bb;
1978 }
1979 /* default case */
1980 if (strncmp(SYMNAME(sptr), "..inline", 8) == 0) {
1981 /* append symbol number to distinguish */
1982 sprintf(b, "%s_%d", SYMNAME(sptr), sptr);
1983 return b;
1984 }
1985 return SYMNAME(sptr);
1986} /* printname */
1987
1988static void
1989_printnme(int n)
1990{
1991 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
1992 if (n < 0 || n >= nmeb.stg_avail) {
1993 putint("nme", n);
1994 return;
1995 }
1996 switch (NME_TYPE(n)) {
1997 case NT_VAR:
1998 appendstring1(printname(NME_SYM(n)));
1999 break;
2000 case NT_MEM:
2001 if (NME_NM(n)) {
2002 _printnme(NME_NM(n));
2003 } else {
2004 appendstring1("Unknown");
2005 }
2006 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
2007 appendstring1(".real");
2008 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 1) {
2009 appendstring1(".imag");
2010 } else
2011 {
2012 appendstring1(".");
2013 appendstring1(printname(NME_SYM(n)));
2014 }
2015 break;
2016 case NT_ARR:
2017 if (NME_NM(n)) {
2018 _printnme(NME_NM(n));
2019 } else {
2020 appendstring1("Unknown");
2021 }
2022 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
2023 appendstring1("[");
2024 appendint1(NME_CNST(n));
2025 appendstring1("]");
2026 } else if (NME_SUB(n) != 0) {
2027 int asdx, i, ndim;
2028 appendstring1("[");
2029 asdx = NME_SUB(n);
2030 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asdx);
2031 for (i = 0; i < ndim; ++i) {
2032 int d;
2033 d = ASD_SUBS(n, i);
2034 printast(d);
2035 if (i)
2036 appendstring1(",");
2037 }
2038 appendstring1("]");
2039 } else {
2040 appendstring1("[?]");
2041 }
2042 break;
2043 case NT_IND:
2044 appendstring1("*(");
2045 if (NME_NM(n)) {
2046 _printnme(NME_NM(n));
2047 } else {
2048 appendstring1("Unknown");
2049 }
2050 if (NME_SYM(n) == NME_NULL) {
2051 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
2052 if (NME_CNST(n)) {
2053 appendstring1("+");
2054 appendint1(NME_CNST(n));
2055 }
2056 } else {
2057 appendstring1("+?");
2058 }
2059 appendstring1(")");
2060 break;
2061 case NT_UNK:
2062 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
2063 appendstring1("unknown");
2064 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 1) {
2065 appendstring1("volatile");
2066 } else {
2067 appendstring1("unknown:");
2068 appendint1(NME_SYM(n));
2069 }
2070 break;
2071 default:
2072 appendstring1("nme(");
2073 appendint1(n);
2074 appendstring1(":");
2075 appendint1(NME_TYPE(n));
2076 appendstring1(")");
2077 break;
2078 }
2079} /* _printnme */
2080
2081void
2082printnme(int n)
2083{
2084 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
2085 putstring1("");
2086 _printnme(n);
2087} /* printnme */
2088
2089void
2090dumpnme(int n)

2341void
2342dstds(int std1, int std2)
2343{
2344 int stdx;
2345 if (std1 <= 0 || std1 >= astb.std.stg_avail)
2346 std1 = STD_NEXT(0);
2347 if (std2 <= 0 || std2 >= astb.std.stg_avail)
2348 std2 = STD_PREV(0);
2349 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
2350 fprintf(dfile, "subprogram %d %s:\n", gbl.func_count, SYMNAME(gbl.currsub));
2351 for (stdx = std1; stdx != 0; stdx = STD_NEXT(stdx)) {
2352 dstd(stdx);
2353 if (stdx == std2)
2354 break;
2355 }
2356} /* dstds */

2395/* dump 'count' before and after stdx */
2396void
2397dstdr(int stdx, int count)
2398{
2399 int s1, s2, c;
2400 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
2401 if (stdx < 0 || stdx >= astb.std.stg_avail) {
2402 fprintf(dfile, "\nstd %d out of range [0:%d)\n", stdx, astb.std.stg_avail);
2403 return;
2404 }
2405 /* go backwards for 'count' */
2406 for (s1 = stdx, c = count; c > 0 && s1 > 0 && s1 <= astb.std.stg_avail;
2407 s1 = STD_PREV(s1), --c)
2408 ;
2409 /* go forwards for 'count' */
2410 for (s2 = stdx, c = count; c > 0 && s2 > 0 && s2 <= astb.std.stg_avail;
2411 s2 = STD_NEXT(s2), --c)
2412 ;
2413 dstds(s1, s2);
2414} /* dstdr */

2420} /* dstda */

2514void
2515puttmplflag(char *s, int f)
2516{

2518 if (f) {
2519 int l = strlen(s);
2520 if (linelen + l >= 79) {
2521 fprintf(dfile, "\n%s", s);
2522 linelen = l;
2523 } else if (linelen > 0) {
2524 fprintf(dfile, " %s", s);
2525 linelen += l + 1;
2526 } else {
2527 fprintf(dfile, "%s", s);
2528 linelen = l;
2529 }
2530 }
2531} /* puttmplflag */

2563void
2564dalnd(int alnd)
2565{
2566 int i, f;
2567 if (alnd == 0)
2568 return;
2569 if (dtb.base == NULL)
2570 return;
2571 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
2572 if (alnd < 0 || alnd >= dtb.avl) {
2573 putline();
2574 fprintf(dfile, "ALND:%d out of bounds 1:%d\n", alnd, dtb.avl);
2575 return;
2576 }
2577 putline();
2578 putint("alnd", alnd);
2579 puttmpltype("type", TMPL_TYPE(alnd));
2580 puttmplsc("alignee_sc", TMPL_ALIGNEE_SC(alnd));
2581 puttmplsc("target_sc", TMPL_TARGET_SC(alnd));
2582 putint("rank", TMPL_RANK(alnd));
2583 f = TMPL_FLAG(alnd);
2584 putbit("sequential", f & __SEQUENTIAL);
2585 f &= ~__SEQUENTIAL;
2586 putbit("assumedsize", f & __ASSUMED_SIZE);
2587 f &= ~__ASSUMED_SIZE;
2588 putbit("assumedshape", f & __ASSUMED_SHAPE);
2589 f &= ~__ASSUMED_SHAPE;
2590 putbit("save", f & __SAVE);
2591 f &= ~__SAVE;
2592 putbit("inherit", f & __INHERIT);
2593 f &= ~__INHERIT;
2594 putbit("dynamic", f & __DYNAMIC);
2595 f &= ~__DYNAMIC;
2596 putbit("pointer", f & __POINTER);
2597 f &= ~__POINTER;
2598 putbit("local", f & __LOCAL);
2599 f &= ~__LOCAL;
2600 putbit("off_template", f & __OFF_TEMPLATE);
2601 f &= ~__OFF_TEMPLATE;
2602 putbit("identify_map", f & __IDENTITY_MAP);
2603 f &= ~__IDENTITY_MAP;
2604 putbit("no_overlaps", f & __NO_OVERLAPS);
2605 f &= ~__NO_OVERLAPS;
2606 putbit("in", f & __INTENT_IN);
2607 f &= ~__INTENT_IN;
2608 putbit("out", f & __INTENT_OUT);
2609 f &= ~__INTENT_OUT;
2610
2611 if ((f & __TRANSCRIPTIVE_DIST_TARGET) == __TRANSCRIPTIVE_DIST_TARGET) {
2612 putstring("disttarget", "transcriptive");
2613 } else if (f & __PRESCRIPTIVE_DIST_TARGET) {
2614 putstring("disttarget", "prescriptive");
2615 } else if (f & __DESCRIPTIVE_DIST_TARGET) {
2616 putstring("disttarget", "descriptive");
2617 } else {
2618 putstring("disttarget", "omitted");
2619 }
2620 f &= ~__TRANSCRIPTIVE_DIST_TARGET;
2621 if ((f & __TRANSCRIPTIVE_DIST_FORMAT) == __TRANSCRIPTIVE_DIST_FORMAT) {
2622 putstring("format", "transcriptive");
2623 } else if (f & __PRESCRIPTIVE_DIST_FORMAT) {
2624 putstring("format", "prescriptive");
2625 } else if (f & __DESCRIPTIVE_DIST_FORMAT) {
2626 putstring("format", "descriptive");
2627 } else {
2628 putstring("format", "omitted");
2629 }
2630 f &= ~__TRANSCRIPTIVE_DIST_FORMAT;
2631 if (f & __PRESCRIPTIVE_ALIGN_TARGET) {
2632 putstring("aligntarget", "prescriptive");
2633 }
2634 f &= ~__PRESCRIPTIVE_ALIGN_TARGET;
2635 if (f & __DESCRIPTIVE_ALIGN_TARGET) {
2636 putstring("aligntarget", "descriptive");
2637 }
2638 f &= ~__DESCRIPTIVE_ALIGN_TARGET;
2639
2640 if (f) {
2641 putnzhex("flag", f);
2642 }
2643 putnzbits("isstar", TMPL_ISSTAR(alnd));
2644 putnzbits("collapse", TMPL_COLLAPSE(alnd));
2645 putline();
2646 putnsym("descr", TMPL_DESCR(alnd));
2647 putnsym("align_target", TMPL_ALIGN_TARGET(alnd));
2648 putnsym("target_descr", TMPL_TARGET_DESCR(alnd));
2649 putnsym("dist_target", TMPL_DIST_TARGET(alnd));
2650 putnsym("dist_target_descr", TMPL_DIST_TARGET_DESCR(alnd));
2651 putline();
2652 for (i = 0; i < TMPL_RANK(alnd); ++i) {
2653 putint("dim", i);
2654 putast("lb", TMPL_LB(alnd, i));
2655 putast("ub", TMPL_UB(alnd, i));
2656 putline();
2657 }
2658} /* dalnd */

2682/* dump one symbol */
2683void
2684dsym(int sptr)
2685{
2686 static char namebuff[210], typebuff[300];
2687 int stype, dtype, alnd, secd, scope;
2688 int i;
2689
2690 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
2691
2692 if (sptr < 0 || sptr >= stb.stg_avail) {
2693 fprintf(dfile, "\nsymbol %d out of %d\n", sptr, stb.stg_avail);
2694 return;
2695 }
2696
2697 BCOPY(stb.stg_base, stb.stg_base + sptr, SYM, 1);
2698
2699 strcpy(namebuff, getprint(sptr));
2700 stype = STYPEG(0);
2701 dtype = DTYPEG(0);
2702 typebuff[0] = '\0';
2703 if (dtype)
2704 getdtype(dtype, typebuff);
2705
2706 fprintf(dfile, "\n%-30.30s %s\n", namebuff, typebuff);
2707 linelen = 0;
2708
2709 putint("sptr", sptr);
2710 putint("dtype", DTYPEG(0));
2711 putsc("sc", SCG(0));
2712 putstype("stype", STYPEG(0));
2713 if (UNAMEG(0)) {
2714 putstring("uname", stb.n_base + UNAMEG(0));
2715 }
2716
2717 putline();
2718 DTYPEP(0, 0);
2719 NMPTRP(0, 0);
2720 SCP(0, 0);
2721 UNAMEP(0, 0);
2722
2723 putsym("enclfunc", ENCLFUNCG(0));
2724 putsym("hashlk", HASHLKG(0));
2725 scope = SCOPEG(0);
2726 if (scope == 0 || scope >= 200) // 200 is largely arbitrary
2727 putsym("scope", SCOPEG(0));
2728 else if (scope == 1)

4222dumphashlk(int sptr)
4223{
4224 int s, n;
4225 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4226 fprintf(dfile, "hash link for %d:%s\n", sptr, SYMNAME(sptr));
4227 n = NMPTRG(sptr);
4228 for (s = first_hash(sptr); s > 1; s = HASHLKG(s)) {
4229 if (NMPTRG(s) == n) {
4230 putline();

4237void
4238dcommon(int c)
4239{
4240 int m;
4241 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4242 if (c <= NOSYM || c >= stb.stg_avail) {
4243 fprintf(dfile, "\ncommon block symbol %d out of %d\n", c, stb.stg_avail);
4244 return;
4245 }
4246 fprintf(dfile, "common/%d:%s/ ", c, SYMNAME(c));
4247 for (m = CMEMFG(c); m > NOSYM; m = SYMLKG(m)) {
4248 if (m != CMEMFG(c))
4249 fprintf(dfile, ", ");
4250 fprintf(dfile, "%d:%s", m, SYMNAME(m));
4251 }
4252 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
4253} /* dcommon */
4254
4255void
4256dcommons()
4257{
4258 int cmn, any;
4259 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4260 if (gbl.cmblks <= NOSYM) {
4261 fprintf(dfile, "Common Block List is Empty\n");
4262 } else {
4263 fprintf(dfile, "Common Block List:\n");
4264 for (cmn = gbl.cmblks; cmn > NOSYM; cmn = SYMLKG(cmn)) {
4265 dcommon(cmn);
4266 }
4267 }
4268 any = 0;
4269 for (cmn = 2; cmn < stb.stg_avail; ++cmn) {
4270 if (STYPEG(cmn) == ST_CMBLK) {
4271 /* find it on the list */
4272 int c;
4273 for (c = gbl.cmblks; c != cmn && c > NOSYM; c = SYMLKG(c))
4274 ;
4275 if (c != cmn) {
4276 /* not found */
4277 if (!any) {
4278 fprintf(dfile, "Not on Common Block List:\n");
4279 }
4280 dcommon(c);
4281 ++any;
4282 }
4283 }
4284 }
4285} /* dcommons */

4287void
4288dumpdt(int dt)
4289{
4290 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4291 if (dt <= 0 || dt >= stb.dt.stg_avail) {
4292 fprintf(dfile, "\ndatatype %d out of %d\n", dt, stb.dt.stg_avail);
4293 return;
4294 }
4295 putint("dtype", dt);
4296 putdty("ty", DTY(dt));
4297 putline();
4298
4299 switch (DTY(dt)) {
4300 case TY_CHAR:
4301 case TY_NCHAR:
4302 putast("len", DTY(dt + 1));
4303 break;
4304 case TY_PTR:
4305 putint("pointee", DTY(dt + 1));
4306 break;
4307 case TY_ARRAY:
4308 putint("element", DTY(dt + 1));
4309 putint("desc", DTY(dt + 2));
4310 if (DTY(dt + 2)) {
4311 int numdim, i;
4312 numdim = ADD_NUMDIM(dt);
4313 putint("numdim", numdim);
4314 putbit("adjarr", ADD_ADJARR(dt));
4315 putbit("assumedsize", ADD_ASSUMSZ(dt));
4316 putbit("assumedshape", ADD_ASSUMSHP(dt));
4317 putbit("assumedrank", ADD_ASSUMRANK(dt));
4318 putbit("defer", ADD_DEFER(dt));
4319 putbit("nobounds", ADD_NOBOUNDS(dt));
4320 putast("zbase", ADD_ZBASE(dt));
4321 putast("numelm", ADD_NUMELM(dt));
4322 if (numdim < 1 || numdim > 7) {
4323 numdim = 0;
4324 }
4325 for (i = 0; i < numdim; ++i) {
4326 putline();
4327 putint("dim", i);
4328 putast("lwbd", ADD_LWBD(dt, i));
4329 putast("upbd", ADD_UPBD(dt, i));
4330 putast("lwast", ADD_LWAST(dt, i));
4331 putast("upast", ADD_UPAST(dt, i));
4332 putast("extntast", ADD_EXTNTAST(dt, i));
4333 putast("mlpyr", ADD_MLPYR(dt, i));
4334 }
4335 }
4336 break;
4337 case TY_STRUCT:
4338 case TY_UNION:
4339 case TY_DERIVED:
4340 putsym("sptr", DTY(dt + 1));
4341 putint("size", DTY(dt + 2));
4342 putsym("tag", DTY(dt + 3));
4343 putint("align", DTY(dt + 4));
4344 putint("ict", DTY(dt + 5));
4345 putline();
4346 putsymlk("members", DTY(dt + 1));
4347 break;
4348 }
4349 putline();
4350 if (dt > 0 && dt < stb.dt.stg_avail && DTY(dt) > 0)
4351 putdtype("type", dt);
4352 putline();
4353} /* dumpdt */
4354

4356dumpdts()

4358 int dt;
4359 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4360 fprintf(dfile, "\n********** DATATYPE TABLE **********\n");
4361 for (dt = 1; dt < stb.dt.stg_avail; dt += dlen(DTY(dt))) {
4362 if (dt) {
4363 fprintf(dfile, "\n");

4367} /* dumpdts */

4381/* hlvect.h */
4382char *
4383getdddir(DDEDGE *dd)
4384{
4385 static char buf[99];
4386 char *p;
4387 int i, dir;
4388 p = buf;
4389 dir = DD_DIRVEC(dd);
4390 for (i = MAX_LOOPS - 1; i >= 0; --i) {
4391 DIRVEC t;
4392 if (p != buf)
4393 *p++ = ',';
4394 t = DIRV_ENTRYG(dir, i);
4395 if (t == DIRV_LT) {
4396 *p++ = '<';
4397 } else if (t == DIRV_EQ) {
4398 *p++ = '=';
4399 } else if (t == DIRV_GT) {
4400 *p++ = '>';
4401 } else if (t == (DIRV_LT | DIRV_EQ)) {
4402 *p++ = '<';
4403 *p++ = '=';
4404 } else if (t == (DIRV_GT | DIRV_EQ)) {
4405 *p++ = '>';
4406 *p++ = '=';
4407 } else if (t == (DIRV_LT | DIRV_GT)) {
4408 *p++ = '<';
4409 *p++ = '>';
4410 } else if (t == (DIRV_LT | DIRV_EQ | DIRV_GT)) {
4411 *p++ = '*';
4412 }
4413 if (t & DIRV_RD)
4414 *p++ = 'R';
4415 }
4416 if (dir & DIRV_ALLEQ) {
4417 *p++ = ',';
4418 *p++ = '=';
4419 *p++ = '=';
4420 }
4421 *p++ = '\0';
4422 return buf;
4423} /* getdddir */
4424
4425void
4426putdd(DDEDGE *dd)
4427{
4428 static const char *types[] = {"flow", "anti", "output", "?3",
4429 "?4", "?5", "?6", "?7"};
4430 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4431 if (dd == NULL) {
4432 fprintf(dfile, "null-dd-edge");
4433 return;
4434 }
4435
4436 sprintf(BUF, "%s (%s) %d", types[DD_TYPE(dd)], getdddir(dd), DD_SINK(dd));
4437 putit();
4438} /* putdd */
4439
